      "id": "PopularPost313070",
      "post_content": "Worth keeping a set for sideboard; sees occasional vintage play (The Mountains Win Again); happens to be the cheapest beater for this kind of effect. Combines well with [Pyrokinesis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyrokinesis) as you can kill up to 4 2/2s, 2 3/3s, or a 5/5 with them combined together. It also keeps you from wasting kinesis on small creatures.  \n  \nGreat for multiplayer. So you can save your bigger wipes for when things get hairy. Run him in a {(u/r)} flying deck? ([Delver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Delver), [wormfang drake](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=wormfang drake), [Ruinator](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ruinator), dragons?)",
      "posted_by": "blurrymadness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost313070\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">Worth keeping a set for sideboard; sees occasional vintage play (The Mountains Win Again); happens to be the cheapest beater for this kind of effect. Combines well with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pyrokinesis\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyrokinesis\">Pyrokinesis</a> as you can kill up to 4 2/2s, 2 3/3s, or a 5/5 with them combined together. It also keeps you from wasting kinesis on small creatures.<br/><br/>Great for multiplayer. So you can save your bigger wipes for when things get hairy. Run him in a {(u/r)} flying deck? (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Delver\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Delver\">Delver</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"wormfang drake\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=wormfang drake\">wormfang drake</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ruinator\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ruinator\">Ruinator</a>, dragons?)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '313070'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44651\">blurrymadness</span>\r\n                                (4/29/2013 11:21:26 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\